Package: fastfocal
Type: Package
Title: Fast Multi-Scale Focal and Extraction Functions for Raster Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ho Yi", "Wan", email = "hoyiwan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Fast and flexible moving window and buffer-based raster extraction
    at user-defined spatial scales. Supports various focal statistics and
    point-based or buffer-based extraction using sf or terra.
